subtitleNullable: True coral snakes vs. false ones (small dataset)
descriptionNullable:
This is the dataset I have used on my preprint: [SnakeFace: a transfer learning based app for snake classification](https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2023.06.13.544741v3)
This is the dataset for separating false coral snakes from true ones.
You can use this dataset to try to replicate the results, using say Python, or following the procedure I have followed on my preprint. 
I have used Teachable Machine (which uses TensorFlow.js).
![](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nIORDZ4MGAk)

**Warning**. the images were collected manually from Google Image, which comes from several sources. They may be protected by copyright.
